      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRYSTAL CROWN (2) hit the ground running off the low draw last start and was never headed (17.12) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 6 over 300m. Will go close again if runs up to latest. SPRINGVALE MARGI (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (20.63) last time in a Grade 6 at this track. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Expected to give a good account. KILCOY LASS (4) was below best last time but prior to that was narrowly beaten when fourth (17.90) in a Grade 6 at Mt Gambier. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. ADA BLAZE (5) was in the money two back in a Grade 6/MDN at Murray Bridge Straight then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when second (17.47) over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight.",
